  "source": "// Demonstrates typed pointer-ABI for account detail and asset transfer.\nseiyaku DetailAndTransfer {\n  kotoage fn set_cursor_and_transfer() permission(Admin) {\n    // Write a small JSON cursor to the caller's account metadata\n    set_account_detail(authority(), name!(\"cursor\"), json!{ q: \"sc_dummy\", c: 1 });\n\n    // Transfer 10 ROSE from Alice to Bob\n    let from = account!(\"sorau’Šø1Np’Šā’ŠĢŃā▒’Šćq11p’Į│’Šś2’Į▒5’Šć’Į”iCJKjR’Šöz’ĮĘNMN’Šå’Į╣’ŠĢPC’Į│’ŠÖFv’ĮĄE9LBLB\");\n    let to = account!(\"sorau’Šø1Nf’ĮĘg’Šē’Šō’ŠēB’Į”K’Šī’Šś’ŠÆo’Šć’Šé’ŠørG81’ŠŗjW’ŠÄ’ŠĢVncw’ŠīS’Į▒3p’Šś’Šŗ’ŠēhUS9Q76\");\n    let asset = asset_definition!(\"6pEP9RjNoZ7beWkT3pLfKoM1dyfi\");\n    transfer_asset(from, to, asset, 10);\n  }\n}\n",
